text: Sebastian Seidl (born 12 July 1990 in Nürtingen) is a German judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 66 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Fabio Basile. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:German male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Germany Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:People from Esslingen (district) Category:European Games competitors for Germany Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in judo Category:European Games bronze medalists for Germany
